highlights.text: “General Zod 2017” by The Snæss Project and Teasjus is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Sweden, up 16 spots at #68.
“The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs Sweden the longest, at 100 days straight.
bob hund has the most spots on Viral Songs Sweden. “Det skulle vara lätt för mig att säga att jag inte… - Vinylljud 2019” is the highest at #30.
“Back to Black - Afro Edit” by Lukas & Frank, Yann Hendriksen, and Vescu is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Sweden at #5.
